<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= app.siteTitle %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN", sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f7f9ff 0%, #eef1ff 100%);
      color: #2f2f2f;
    }
    main {
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 2rem;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 35px rgba(86, 110, 255, 0.15);
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    p {
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .counter {
      margin-top: 1.25rem;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      background: #f2f4ff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(79, 108, 255, 0.25);
    }
    .counter h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #4f6cff;
    }
    .counter-content {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.25rem;
      margin-top: 0.75rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .count-circle {
      width: 110px;
      height: 110px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #ffffff 0%, #d9e2ff 100%);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #1d2a6d;
      font-weight: 600;
      box-shadow: inset 0 6px 12px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6), 0 10px 22px rgba(61, 83, 208, 0.2);
    }
    .count-circle span {
      font-size: 2.6rem;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .progress {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 220px;
    }
    .progress-bar {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      height: 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(79, 108, 255, 0.2);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .progress-bar span {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      border-radius: inherit;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4f6cff 0%, #8c9dff 100%);
      transition: width 0.3s ease;
      width: 0;
    }
    .progress-bar span.fill-0 { width: 0%; }
    .progress-bar span.fill-5 { width: 5%; }
    .progress-bar span.fill-10 { width: 10%; }
    .progress-bar span.fill-15 { width: 15%; }
    .progress-bar span.fill-20 { width: 20%; }
    .progress-bar span.fill-25 { width: 25%; }
    .progress-bar span.fill-30 { width: 30%; }
    .progress-bar span.fill-35 { width: 35%; }
    .progress-bar span.fill-40 { width: 40%; }
    .progress-bar span.fill-45 { width: 45%; }
    .progress-bar span.fill-50 { width: 50%; }
    .progress-bar span.fill-55 { width: 55%; }
    .progress-bar span.fill-60 { width: 60%; }
    .progress-bar span.fill-65 { width: 65%; }
    .progress-bar span.fill-70 { width: 70%; }
    .progress-bar span.fill-75 { width: 75%; }
    .progress-bar span.fill-80 { width: 80%; }
    .progress-bar span.fill-85 { width: 85%; }
    .progress-bar span.fill-90 { width: 90%; }
    .progress-bar span.fill-95 { width: 95%; }
    .progress-bar span.fill-100 { width: 100%; }
    .progress-note {
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #5b6cb2;
    }
    footer {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #6c6c80;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <% const fillPercent = Math.min(app.visitCount * 5, 100); %>
  <% const fillStep = Math.round(fillPercent / 5) * 5; %>
  <% const fillClass = `fill-${fillStep}`; %>
  <% const fillPercentText = `${fillStep}%`; %>
  <main>
    <h1><%= app.siteTitle %></h1>
    <p><%= app.sharedMessage %></p>
    <div class="counter">
      <h2>アクセスカウンター</h2>
      <div class="counter-content">
        <div class="count-circle">
          <span><%= app.visitCount %></span>
          <small>アクセス</small>
        </div>
        <div class="progress">
          <div class="progress-bar">
            <span class="<%= fillClass %>"></span>
          </div>
          <p class="progress-note"></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p>ページを再読み込みするとカウントが増え、同じ変数が共有されていることが分かります。</p>
    <footer></footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
